    support: Add xdup
    
    Add xdup as the error-checking version of dup for test cases.
    
    Signed-off-by: Siddhesh Poyarekar <siddhesh@sourceware.org>
    Reviewed-by: Adhemerval Zanella  <adhemerval.zanella@linaro.org>

